url": ""}, {"cid": 2540317, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 485083, "reply_to": 2540243, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 嗯确实。dz的感觉就是他好像每句话我都可以理性上理解但是感性上不太认同……比如说他表达出来很欣赏希腊最无用的科学我实在是不太能理解，可能还是境界比较低_(:3」∠)_", "timestamp": 1631978093, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2540336, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 485083, "reply_to": 2540317, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 多听听就会感受到吴老师的人格魅力了", "timestamp": 1631978216, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2540361, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 485083, "reply_to": 2540317, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 欣赏无用的科学是有很久远思想溯源的。包括现在的理论数学理论物理都有这样的倾向", "timestamp": 1631978315, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2540374, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 485083, "reply_to": 2540317, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 对待这样一门学科还是要有一点敬畏的，不能先入为主太小看了人家", "timestamp": 1631978419, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2540602, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 485083, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还好我没听几节课", "timestamp": 1631979803, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2540632, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 485083, "reply_to": 2540374, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 不算小看吧，是单纯的和老师有不同的观点而已啦。", "timestamp": 1631980061, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2540653, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 485083, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "hhhhh吴老师讲得确实还行 但是“人格魅力”……可以了解一些相关八卦", "timestamp": 1631980175, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 485083, "reply": 24, "tag": null, "text": "退科学通史吗\n缺一门RW，但是老师的公知言论让我有点yue……课也听不进去", "timestamp": 1631971938, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1631980174, "url": "", "vote": {}}}